    "De Premium-aankoop verloopt volledig via Apple's App Store. Wij ontvangen geen betaalgegevens. Apple kan je bonnetje en aankoopstatus delen met de app — die gebruiken we alleen om Premium-functies te ontgrendelen. Family Sharing-leden krijgen automatisch toegang via Apple's eigen mechanisme." : {
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "The Premium purchase goes entirely through Apple's App Store. We don't receive any payment details. Apple may share your receipt and purchase status with the app — we use those only to unlock Premium features. Family Sharing members get automatic access via Apple's own mechanism."
          }
        }
      }
    },
