    },
    "Premium-gebruikers met iCloud ingeschakeld kunnen hun Youniquelist synchroniseren tussen hun eigen Apple-apparaten via Apple's SwiftData/CloudKit. Dit gebeurt versleuteld via je eigen Apple-ID — wij hebben er geen toegang toe. Family Sharing-leden behouden hun eigen iCloud en zien dus hun eigen favorieten, niet die van anderen." : {
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Premium users with iCloud enabled can sync their Youniquelist across their own Apple devices via Apple's SwiftData/CloudKit. This is encrypted via your own Apple ID — we have no access to it. Family Sharing members keep their own iCloud, so they see their own favorites, not anyone else's."
          }
        }
      }
